        <b class="Bold">NOTE:</b> The organization needs to contact their FireLight<sup MadCap:conditions="General.Online">®</sup> Strategic Account Manager to have the CSS modified to display the option to sign with the Topaz signature tablet.<p><b class="Bold">Install the Topaz Plug-In</b></p><ol><li>Note the model number on the bottom of the Topaz tablet.</li><li>Connect the Topaz tablet to your device (laptop, etc.).</li><li>Create a new application in FireLight.</li><li>Complete Form Entry and continue to Signatures.</li><li>Click <b class="Bold">Agent</b> in the <b class="Bold">List of Required Signers</b> and review and approve the application.</li><li>Click <b class="Bold">Sign</b> to open the Agent On-Site Signature page.</li><li><p>Click the information icon <img src="../../ImagesAdmin/InformationMsgIcon.png" alt="Informational Message Icon" title="Informational Message Icon" />  on the right of the <b class="Bold">Sign with Topaz® signature tablet</b> link.</p><p><img src="../../ImagesUserGuide/PreferencesTraningMsgs/Capture44.png" alt="Sign with Topaz Signature Tablet Link" title="Sign with Topaz Signature Tablet Link" /></p></li><li><p>In the dialog, click the link to install the SigWeb® Software.</p><p><img src="../../ImagesUserGuide/PreferencesTraningMsgs/Capture45.png" alt="Install SigWeb for Topaz Tablet" title="Install SigWeb for Topaz Tablet" /></p></li><li><p>The Topaz Systems website opens. Click the link to the <b class="Bold">SigWeb Installation Help Guide</b> for step-by-step installation instructions.</p><p class="note"><b class="Bold">IMPORTANT!</b> If the Topaz HTTPS certificate expires, the Topaz signature pad will not work. To update the certificate, go to <a href="http://www.topazsystems.com/sigweb.html" target="_blank" title="http://www.topazsystems.com/sigweb.html" alt="http://www.topazsystems.com/sigweb.html">http://www.topazsystems.com/sigweb.html</a> and follow directions in the webpage to update your Topaz certificate by downloading the SigWeb Certificate Updater.</p></li><li><p>After installing the Topaz signature pad: In FireLight, fill in the remaining information on the Agent On-Site Signature page, click the <b class="Bold">Sign with Topaz® signature tablet</b> link, and sign on the Topaz signature tablet to sign your signature in FireLight.</p><p><img src="../../ImagesUserGuide/PreferencesTraningMsgs/Capture46.png" alt="Use Topaz Signature Tablet to Sign" title="Use Topaz Signature Tablet to Sign" /></p></li></ol></body>
</html>